name: {DD} Missionary sex frames
description:
I haven't overtrained this one, to make it possible to use with my DGPD model with larger variety of prompts. But it still works pretty with lots of other models. If you struggle to get grids, use my model to get you a grid in txt2img, that use ultimateSD upscale or just img2img it with higher resolution.

I'll make overtrained one later too for those who won't be able to make grids even with my model.

You can read a manual about how to use it from here.

Tags

2x2frames, 3x3frames

Additional tags

series of images of POV missionary sex

Properties

  • Clip skip: 2;

  • Resolution: 512x512 (for 2x2frames) and 768x768 (for 3x3frames). IT"S MANDATORY!

  • models: DGPD, perfectDeliberate, hyperHeaven, dreamShape - worked the best for me;

*Consider trying to use hires fix with x3, x4 scale and denoising str 0.4-0.6. Consistency is much higher that way.

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)

Also my wet hair Lora was banned here, I dunno why. You can download the last version of it from my patreon for free.
